about.summary: A JupyterLab extension for the rendering transient-display-data messages

name: jupyterlab-transient-display-data
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "jupyterlab-transient-display-data" %}
{% set version = "0.3.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:

  url: https://github.com/vatlab/transient-display-data/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 3100e31e265a1ba169ec693058f4b00980176343c3090a959b139e865ab517a8

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python

requirements:
  build:
    - nodejs
  host:
    - jupyterlab
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - jupyterlab
    - nodejs
    - python >=3.5

test:
  commands:
    - jupyter labextension list | grep transient-display-data  # [unix]
    - jupyter labextension list | findstr transient-display-data  # [win]
    - jupyter lab build

about:
  home: https://github.com/vatlab/transient-display-data
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A JupyterLab extension for the rendering transient-display-data messages
  dev_url: https://github.com/vatlab/transient-display-data

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - BoPeng
